    "body": "<!DOCTYPE html><html lang=\"en\"><head><meta charset=\"UTF-8\"><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0\"><title>Command Centre is Live</title></head><body style=\"margin:0;padding:0;background:#06080f;font-family:'Helvetica Neue',Arial,sans-serif;color:#e2e8f0;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;\"><table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"background:#06080f;\"><tr><td align=\"center\" style=\"padding:40px 16px;\"><table role=\"presentation\" width=\"600\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"max-width:600px;width:100%;background:#0a0e1a;border:1px solid rgba(99,102,241,0.15);border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden;\"><tr><td style=\"padding:48px 40px 0;text-align:center;\"><div style=\"display:inline-block;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#6366f1,#8b5cf6);-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;font-size:28px;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:-0.02em;\">SECOND MIND HQ</div></td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:40px 40px 0;\"><h1 style=\"margin:0 0 8px;font-size:32px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-0.03em;line-height:1.2;color:#ffffff;text-align:center;\">Command Centre is live.</h1><p style=\"margin:0 0 32px;color:#94a3b8;font-size:16px;text-align:center;line-height:1.6;\">The first autonomous AI operating system for business.</p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:0 40px;\"><p style=\"margin:0 0 24px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.7;color:#e2e8f0;\">Hi {{first_name}},</p><p style=\"margin:0 0 24px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.7;color:#e2e8f0;\">We just launched something different. Not a chatbot. Not another SaaS dashboard. A full command centre where <strong style=\"color:#ffffff;\">28 AI agents</strong> run your operations \u2014 marketing, research, revenue, accounting, customer outreach \u2014 while you focus on strategy.</p><table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:0 0 32px;\"><tr><td style=\"padding:20px 24px;background:rgba(99,102,241,0.08);border:1px solid rgba(99,102,241,0.15);border-radius:12px;\"><table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr><td style=\"padding:6px 0;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;color:#e2e8f0;\"><span style=\"color:#6366f1;font-weight:700;\">&#x25CF;</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong style=\"color:#fff;\">28 autonomous agents</strong> \u2014 research, content, email, payments, social</td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:6px 0;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;color:#e2e8f0;\"><span style=\"color:#22c55e;font-weight:700;\">&#x25CF;</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong style=\"color:#fff;\">Live dashboard</strong> \u2014 watch every agent in real time</td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:6px 0;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;color:#e2e8f0;\"><span style=\"color:#f59e0b;font-weight:700;\">&#x25CF;</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong style=\"color:#fff;\">Revenue engine</strong> \u2014 Stripe, email campaigns, landing pages, all automated</td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:6px 0;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;color:#e2e8f0;\"><span style=\"color:#06b6d4;font-weight:700;\">&#x25CF;</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong style=\"color:#fff;\">Self-improving</strong> \u2014 agents learn from each cycle and get smarter</td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:6px 0;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;color:#e2e8f0;\"><span style=\"color:#8b5cf6;font-weight:700;\">&#x25CF;</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong style=\"color:#fff;\">Production-ready</strong> \u2014 hosted SaaS, no setup headaches</td></tr></table></td></tr></table><p style=\"margin:0 0 24px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.7;color:#e2e8f0;\">People are already using Command Centre to run their entire back office. One founder replaced 3 freelancers. Another generated <strong style=\"color:#22c55e;\">$4,200 in the first week</strong> from automated campaigns.</p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:0 40px 32px;\"><table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:0 0 24px;\"><tr><td style=\"padding:14px 20px;background:rgba(17,24,39,0.8);border:1px solid rgba(99,102,241,0.12);border-radius:10px;font-size:14px;\"><table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr><td style=\"padding:4px 0;color:#e2e8f0;\"><strong style=\"color:#6366f1;\">Solo</strong> \u2014 $49/mo &rarr; 1 seat, core agents, basic dashboards</td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:4px 0;color:#e2e8f0;\"><strong style=\"color:#22c55e;\">Team</strong> \u2014 $149/mo &rarr; 5 seats, full agent roster, custom spawning</td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:4px 0;color:#e2e8f0;\"><strong style=\"color:#06b6d4;\">Enterprise</strong> \u2014 $499/mo &rarr; Unlimited seats, custom agents, SLA</td></tr></table></td></tr></table><table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr><td align=\"center\"><a href=\"https://secondmindhq.com/pricing?utm_source=email&utm_medium=drip&utm_campaign=aihq_launch_mar2026&utm_content=email1\" style=\"display:inline-block;padding:16px 40px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#6366f1,#8b5cf6);color:#ffffff;font-size:16px;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;border-radius:12px;letter-spacing:0.02em;\">Get started now &rarr;</a></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:32px 40px;border-top:1px solid rgba(99,102,241,0.1);\"><p style=\"margin:0 0 4px;font-size:14px;color:#94a3b8;\">Welcome to the future of work.</p><p style=\"margin:0 0 16px;font-size:14px;color:#94a3b8;font-weight:600;\">\u2014 The Second Mind HQ Team</p><p style=\"margin:0;font-size:12px;color:#475569;\"><a href=\"https://secondmindhq.com\" style=\"color:#6366f1;text-decoration:none;\">secondmindhq.com</a> &nbsp;|&nbsp; <a href=\"{{unsubscribe_url}}\" style=\"color:#475569;text-decoration:underline;\">Unsubscribe</a></p></td></tr></table></td></tr></table></body></html>"
