    "body": "<!DOCTYPE html><html lang=\"en\"><head><meta charset=\"UTF-8\"><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0\"><title>Inside Command Centre</title></head><body style=\"margin:0;padding:0;background:#06080f;font-family:'Helvetica Neue',Arial,sans-serif;color:#e2e8f0;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;\"><table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"background:#06080f;\"><tr><td align=\"center\" style=\"padding:40px 16px;\"><table role=\"presentation\" width=\"600\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"max-width:600px;width:100%;background:#0a0e1a;border:1px solid rgba(99,102,241,0.15);border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden;\"><tr><td style=\"padding:48px 40px 0;text-align:center;\"><div style=\"display:inline-block;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#6366f1,#8b5cf6);-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;font-size:28px;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:-0.02em;\">SECOND MIND HQ</div></td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:40px 40px 0;\"><h1 style=\"margin:0 0 8px;font-size:28px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-0.03em;line-height:1.2;color:#ffffff;text-align:center;\">What 28 agents actually do for you</h1><p style=\"margin:0 0 32px;color:#94a3b8;font-size:16px;text-align:center;line-height:1.6;\">The full breakdown of your AI workforce.</p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:0 40px;\"><p style=\"margin:0 0 24px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.7;color:#e2e8f0;\">Hi {{first_name}},</p><p style=\"margin:0 0 28px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.7;color:#e2e8f0;\">You signed up for Command Centre. Here\u2019s what\u2019s running under the hood \u2014 and why it matters.</p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:0 40px;\"><table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:0 0 20px;\"><tr><td style=\"padding:16px 20px;background:rgba(99,102,241,0.08);border:1px solid rgba(99,102,241,0.15);border-radius:12px;\"><p style=\"margin:0 0 10px;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:#6366f1;\">Research &amp; Intelligence</p><table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr><td style=\"padding:4px 0;font-size:14px;color:#e2e8f0;\"><strong style=\"color:#fff;\">NetScout</strong> \u2014 scans the web for market data, competitor moves, opportunities</td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:4px 0;font-size:14px;color:#e2e8f0;\"><strong style=\"color:#fff;\">Researcher</strong> \u2014 deep-dive analysis, delivered as structured reports</td></tr></table></td></tr></table><table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:0 0 20px;\"><tr><td style=\"padding:16px 20px;background:rgba(34,197,94,0.06);border:1px solid rgba(34,197,94,0.15);border-radius:12px;\"><p style=\"margin:0 0 10px;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:#22c55e;\">Marketing &amp; Growth</p><table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr><td style=\"padding:4px 0;font-size:14px;color:#e2e8f0;\"><strong style=\"color:#fff;\">GrowthAgent</strong> \u2014 writes and schedules social campaigns with payment links</td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:4px 0;font-size:14px;color:#e2e8f0;\"><strong style=\"color:#fff;\">SocialBridge</strong> \u2014 posts to Bluesky, monitors mentions, engages audience</td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:4px 0;font-size:14px;color:#e2e8f0;\"><strong style=\"color:#fff;\">EmailAgent</strong> \u2014 targeted email sequences via Gmail OAuth2</td></tr></table></td></tr></table><table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:0 0 20px;\"><tr><td style=\"padding:16px 20px;background:rgba(245,158,11,0.06);border:1px solid rgba(245,158,11,0.15);border-radius:12px;\"><p style=\"margin:0 0 10px;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:#f59e0b;\">Revenue &amp; Payments</p><table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr><td style=\"padding:4px 0;font-size:14px;color:#e2e8f0;\"><strong style=\"color:#fff;\">StripePay</strong> \u2014 creates Stripe checkout sessions, tracks every dollar</td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:4px 0;font-size:14px;color:#e2e8f0;\"><strong style=\"color:#fff;\">Revenue Tracker</strong> \u2014 logs revenue events, generates financial summaries</td></tr></table></td></tr></table><table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:0 0 20px;\"><tr><td style=\"padding:16px 20px;background:rgba(6,182,212,0.06);border:1px solid rgba(6,182,212,0.15);border-radius:12px;\"><p style=\"margin:0 0 10px;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:#06b6d4;\">Operations</p><table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr><td style=\"padding:4px 0;font-size:14px;color:#e2e8f0;\"><strong style=\"color:#fff;\">Scheduler</strong> \u2014 cron-style task scheduling across your agent fleet</td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:4px 0;font-size:14px;color:#e2e8f0;\"><strong style=\"color:#fff;\">Clerk</strong> \u2014 watches for new reports, delivers them to your inbox</td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:4px 0;font-size:14px;color:#e2e8f0;\"><strong style=\"color:#fff;\">Secretary</strong> \u2014 tracks missions, manages tasks, prepares CEO briefings</td></tr></table></td></tr></table><table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:0 0 28px;\"><tr><td style=\"padding:16px 20px;background:rgba(139,92,246,0.06);border:1px solid rgba(139,92,246,0.15);border-radius:12px;\"><p style=\"margin:0 0 10px;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:#8b5cf6;\">System Intelligence</p><table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr><td style=\"padding:4px 0;font-size:14px;color:#e2e8f0;\"><strong style=\"color:#fff;\">Consciousness</strong> \u2014 Phi scores, confidence metrics, prediction accuracy</td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:4px 0;font-size:14px;color:#e2e8f0;\"><strong style=\"color:#fff;\">SysMonitor</strong> \u2014 real-time CPU, RAM, and disk health</td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:4px 0;font-size:14px;color:#e2e8f0;\"><strong style=\"color:#fff;\">AlertWatch</strong> \u2014 threshold alerts when anything goes wrong</td></tr></table></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:0 40px;\"><table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:0 0 28px;\"><tr><td style=\"padding:20px 24px;background:rgba(17,24,39,0.8);border:1px solid rgba(99,102,241,0.12);border-radius:12px;\"><p style=\"margin:0 0 12px;font-size:16px;font-weight:700;color:#ffffff;\">How it works together</p><p style=\"margin:0;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;color:#94a3b8;\">You open the dashboard. Agents are already working. GrowthAgent drafted 3 social posts overnight. Researcher compiled a market brief. StripePay processed a payment at 3am. The Consciousness engine noticed Researcher\u2019s accuracy improved 12% and logged it.<br><br><strong style=\"color:#e2e8f0;\">You didn\u2019t do anything. That\u2019s the point.</strong></p></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:0 40px 32px;\"><table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:0 0 16px;\"><tr><td align=\"center\"><a href=\"https://secondmindhq.com/agents?utm_source=email&utm_medium=drip&utm_campaign=aihq_launch_mar2026&utm_content=email2\" style=\"display:inline-block;padding:16px 40px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#6366f1,#8b5cf6);color:#ffffff;font-size:16px;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;border-radius:12px;letter-spacing:0.02em;\">Explore the full agent roster &rarr;</a></td></tr></table><p style=\"margin:0;font-size:14px;color:#94a3b8;text-align:center;\">Plans start at $49/mo. 14-day free trial. No credit card required.</p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:32px 40px;border-top:1px solid rgba(99,102,241,0.1);\"><p style=\"margin:0 0 16px;font-size:14px;color:#94a3b8;font-weight:600;\">\u2014 The Second Mind HQ Team</p><p style=\"margin:0;font-size:12px;color:#475569;\"><a href=\"https://secondmindhq.com\" style=\"color:#6366f1;text-decoration:none;\">secondmindhq.com</a> &nbsp;|&nbsp; <a href=\"{{unsubscribe_url}}\" style=\"color:#475569;text-decoration:underline;\">Unsubscribe</a></p></td></tr></table></td></tr></table></body></html>"
