em>Monitors Phi scores and prediction accuracy across the fleet.</em></p></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:0 40px;\"><table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:0 0 28px;\"><tr><td style=\"padding:20px 24px;background:rgba(17,24,39,0.8);border:1px solid rgba(99,102,241,0.12);border-radius:12px;\"><p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.08em;color:#6366f1;\">The numbers so far</p><table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr><td style=\"padding:6px 0;font-size:14px;color:#e2e8f0;\"><strong style=\"color:#22c55e;\">4 minutes</strong> \u2014 average setup time</td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:6px 0;font-size:14px;color:#e2e8f0;\"><strong style=\"color:#22c55e;\">16 agents</strong> \u2014 average running per user</td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:6px 0;font-size:14px;color:#e2e8f0;\"><strong style=\"color:#22c55e;\">GrowthAgent</strong> \u2014 most-used agent</td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:6px 0;font-size:14px;color:#e2e8f0;\"><strong style=\"color:#22c55e;\">$18,700+</strong> \u2014 revenue generated by users in week 1</td></tr></table></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:0 40px;\"><table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:0 0 20px;\"><tr><td style=\"padding:20px 24px;background:rgba(245,158,11,0.08);border:1px solid rgba(245,158,11,0.2);border-radius:12px;text-align:center;\"><p style=\"margin:0 0 4px;font-size:18px;font-weight:800;color:#f59e0b;\">Early access is limited</p><p style=\"margin:0;font-size:14px;color:#94a3b8;\">We\u2019re capping launch seats to ensure quality. Once they\u2019re gone, the waitlist reopens.</p></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:0 40px 8px;\"><table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:0 0 24px;\"><tr><td style=\"padding:14px 20px;backgroun